f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba9097c1fc5440a7d77a83e858b6da2aa42a6946","tid":1143313,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T20:53:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24a309d3f1fbbd35b04bfc97bfbcff6e458d39e0","tid":1143313,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T21:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64929705d195b254c593544d9578e8c2ec237596","tid":1143313,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T21:10:48.000Z","msg":"天滅中共，天滅中南海"},{"pid":"ec6432a2c01acbb31182f50cf428044e83539d48","tid":1143313,"uid":18245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0a7eb82325ae451ed804efb64fd62ef01b42f35e","tid":1143313,"uid":135522,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:03:32.000Z","msg":"義士加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T22:04:56.000Z","msg":"每個香港人都有責任"},{"pid":"1103cbba70536ba09b1d2938239fe9dde9a525d3","tid":1143313,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T22:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be00dbbdc5e389d44dda4b8cc5b5d14641665969","tid":1143313,"uid":27909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T22:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67307b37f78929d86ab9feef096624d18f2e7165","tid":1143313,"uid":60635,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T22:33:15.000Z","msg":"人地17歲都睇到咁通透，香港堆泛民黃絲係咪智力有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji