係始料不及"},{"pid":"d99bf6d63434e72a7fc69c6a9d5c8b83d297dec1","tid":1143313,"uid":44525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:05:59.000Z","msg":"林榮基好似有份叫佢返黎受審"},{"pid":"742ea36e62c863bc4087e60e15f69b398f85706d","tid":1143313,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81c163ba93a2ca440a9f930b883c56209e81fd2","tid":1143313,"uid":154533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:47:11.000Z","msg":"希望一直有人幫佢la 唔係都幾慘"},{"pid":"121816b4d464bd0350423df974009c65c3cf6285","tid":1143313,"uid":207208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T05:05:22.000Z","msg":"反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰<br />\n<br />\n5月11日 星期六 早上8點半<br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)"},{"pid":"ec9ba6f82d0e1f10bab5b0b0ead31ade8dabc709","tid":1143313,"uid":135007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6efaa8bc4c70ab624e6e6e514e79b5b7d4ed4071","tid":1143313,"uid":36120,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"2212f9af83e4ac604d86abb1f7be284a68911665","tid":1143313,"uid":23993,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d4e5d88a8ff623c807e55ce3546c03feac7d0537","tid":1143313,"uid":36120,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T02:03:37.000Z","msg":"唔係正正就係有法治，所以先可以用法律告到旺角幾個人坐監嗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔根條例無行晒成個司法程序亂咁判先叫人治"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T02:06:43.000Z","msg":"上有釋法<br />\n下有收編下級裁判官<br />\n仲信有險可守？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T02:17:29.000Z","msg":"無得話收唔收編，裁判官就算係點嘅人都只可以按控罪容許嘅範圍去判案，判到乜視乎檢控一方告你乜<br />\n<br />\n話香港無法治真係好天真，因為人地依家就係用晒成個法律程序去煮你，無法治嘅話邊度有呢啲遊戲規則 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n倒不如話自己理解錯咗法治 = 公義好過，法律本身唔係保護有理想嘅人，而只要要嚟 judge 人有無犯咗規"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T05:11:39.000Z","msg":"你呢種法治觀念咪同中共嘅依法而治一鳩樣囉，根據佢哋嘅規則去捉顛覆政權嘅人都係按晒法律條例㗎，問題係中共本身套法律就有缺陷，盲目依住咁嘅規則去judge咪違反法治。你講緊嘅有法可依同埋依法而治，只係法治最低嘅層次，法治係應該有以法達義嘅功能，即係彰顯到正義呀"},{"pid":"c1eef1a92876f07647f23f446fe9e7a43fbb8430","tid":1143313,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T05:18:00.000Z","msg":"搵條台灣仔嫁左佢，搞大埋個肚，攞永久居民身份，唔係過左引渡法好快就要番香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2273688fbe253df3ff8bbf077b09ef15fa9906b","tid":1143313,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T05:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a65124863b3f6a070a112cf00aca5c9462354a","tid":1143313,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T05:50:36.000Z","msg":"思路清𥇦到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林榮基仲話諗住勤佢返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a458f65c71b8cc0af0a8425a05801620d8c807a","tid":1143313,"uid":242672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7fa1c1a20b95689858790e48608a62b51e4e7b4","tid":1143313,"uid":45914,"like":7,"dislike":134,"score":-127,"quote":{"pid":"b1abd9398fd4fb650a202ec6740f982b73319f9c","tid":1143313,"uid":34336,"like":8,"dislike":15,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:11:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:45:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:35